CustomSql.Name: Lynx Federated
CustomSql.SqlQuery:
select 
    c.uid, 
    case when s.use_detailed_entry_menu = 0 then 'No' else 'Yes' end as use_detailed_entry_menu
from source__aurora_federated__lynx.competition c 
inner join source__aurora_federated__lynx.competition_entry_menu_setting s on c.id = s.competition_id
